title: Are you interested in improving?
body:
Watching a higher elo player, in a lower elo, can help players understand what it takes to improve.

If you're interested in watching a Diamond 2-3 player (Top 400 at the beginning of season), please let me know.

I would stream on twitch and play on an old Silver account (plenty of champs). Can try fun builds, education commentary, and will be active in chat for any questions.

Can also duo with viewers.
